---
alwaysApply: true
description: >
  Enforce best practices for configuration management in the codebase.
  - All configuration structs must be defined in the internal/config package.
  - Default values must be sourced from internal/envvars/defaults.go.
  - All configuration loading must use environment variables with sane defaults.
  - Configuration must be validated on startup; fail fast on invalid config.
  - No hardcoded config values outside internal/config and internal/envvars.
  - Document all config options in docs/configuration.md.

